# Environment Variables for Vercel

## Required Variables

### Database (Vercel Postgres)
POSTGRES_URL=
POSTGRES_PRISMA_URL=
POSTGRES_URL_NO_SSL=
POSTGRES_URL_NON_POOLING=
POSTGRES_USER=
POSTGRES_HOST=
POSTGRES_PASSWORD=
POSTGRES_DATABASE=

## Optional Variables

### Analytics
NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_ID=

### AI Chat (if using)
ABACUSAI_API_KEY=

## How to Set Up

1. Go to Vercel Dashboard > Storage > Create Database > Postgres
2. Copy all POSTGRES_* variables to your .env.local for testing
3. Add them to Vercel project settings > Environment Variables
4. Deploy

## Notes
- SQLite is not suitable for Vercel (read-only filesystem)
- Vercel Postgres is the recommended solution
- Connection pooling is handled automatically
